    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Current Platform Support</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">A platform manifest is selected from the model name as lower(model) + &quot;_platform.json&quot; (for example, DS10 gives <text styleclass="Code Example">ds10_platform.json</text>). The table below summarizes current status. &quot;Validated&quot; means the platform has been driven to the SRM <text styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;</text> prompt in EmulatR.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
