    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">A missing platform file is a hard error -- there is no silent fallback. The selection order is: <text styleclass="Code Example">EMULATR_PLATFORM_CONFIG</text>, then a <text styleclass="Code Example">platformConfigPath</text> ini key, then the derived name.</para>
